"I thank the Bulgaria Parliament, MPs from the coat of arms," We continue changes "," Movements for Rights and Freedom "," There is such a people "for today's vitalization in support of Ukraine. Bulgaria and Ukraine deserve a strong friendship mutually beneficial cooperation," he wrote Kuleba [in Twitter.](https://twitter.com/DmytroKuleba/status/1676942020445609985)*!(https://www.ukrinform.ua/rubric-polytics/3732312-zelenskij-ogolosiv-pro-domovlenosti-z-bolgarieu-v-oboronnomu-sektori.html)Voting coincided with a one -day visit to Sofia President of Ukraine Zelensky.

